sub_topic: Identifying the automorphism group of a graph.
message_1: Consider a graph with 6 vertices and 7 edges. Identify the automorphism group of the graph.
message_2:
To identify the automorphism group of the graph, we need to know the structure of the graph. Since there are multiple possible graphs with 6 vertices and 7 edges, we cannot determine the automorphism group without more information.

Please provide more information about the graph, such as adjacency matrix, adjacency list, or a description of the graph's structure.
